commit.message:
Fix wrong suggestion in `WHILE_LET_LOOP`

Ok, I lied in the title. This basically *removes* the problematic part
but:
  1) it was ugly with big bodies;
  2) it was not indented properly;
  3) it wasn’t very smart (see #675).

